content: wtfsayo: Merged 11 PRs this week, with significant contributions including adding a monorepo command to CLI (#4112, +93 lines), fixing Twitter plugin issues (#4108, +2141/-1880 lines), and implementing agent secret salting (#4056, +1373/-234 lines).
